<h1 style="color: #c0392b;">Reservation Rejected</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @reservation.customer_name %>,</p>

<p>
  We regret to inform you that your reservation at
  <strong><%= @reservation.restaurant.name %></strong>
  on <%= @reservation.reservation_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
  at <%= @reservation.reservation_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> has been rejected.
</p>

<p>
  If you have any questions, feel free to contact us. We hope to serve you in the future.
</p>

<p>Thank you,<br>
The <%= @reservation.restaurant.name %> Team</p>